short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Use this app to check for new exams for all your enrolled courses in BrightSpace.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
OsiRegisterer is created for students at the Delft University of Technology (unofficially). OsiRegisterer can be used to manage the registrations of exams of courses to which you are enrolled to in BrightSpace.

Please note that OsiRegisterer does not provide any guarantee that you are actually registered for the exam. For this, please check yourself in Osiris.
